WEBVTT

00:00:58.872 --> 00:01:02.397
sapun.

00:01:02.397 --> 00:01:03.829
Pranje ruku sapunom,

00:01:03.829 --> 00:01:06.200
navika koju uzimamo zdravo za gotovo,

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.484
može smanjiti incidenciju proljeva u pola, 


00:01:08.484 --> 00:01:12.140
reducirati dišne infekcije za jednu trećinu. 


00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:13.911
Pranje ruku sapunom

00:01:13.911 --> 00:01:15.560
može imati utjecaj

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:20.587
na redukciju gripe, trahome, SARSa,

00:01:20.587 --> 00:01:22.977
i u zadnje vrijeme u slučaju kolere,

00:01:22.977 --> 00:01:25.667
i izbijanja ebole,

00:01:25.667 --> 00:01:27.358
jedna od ključnih intervencija

00:01:27.358 --> 00:01:30.176
jest pranje ruku sapunom.